metrics_conclusion: Like A Rolling Stone has higher complexity than the average song  in terms Chord-Bass Melody.
key_conclusion:
Like A Rolling Stone is written in the key of C Major.  

According to the Theorytab database, it is the most common key in all of popular music. 

See the C Major Cheat Sheet for popular chords, chord progressions, downloadable midi files and more!

metadata.editComments: The harmony follows a step-wise diatonic movement from I to V and later vice versa
